{"tid":1198881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"決定好罷工未？作為老師嘅我，約定大家6.12見！","createTime":"2019-06-10T10:48:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:27:41.000Z","uid":26320,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9c2c63f3c3489b35d2561367b36b317fab89088d","tid":1198881,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:48:13.000Z","msg":"未必人人都可以好輕鬆咁罷到工，屋企等你份人工開飯嘅，無辦法㗎，我明，我好明我屋企都等住我開飯，我咁明顯係嚟日請假，作為年約嘅我，係學校表明立場，都好大影響。<br />\n<br />\n但係多你一個唔多？少你一個真係好少！<br />\n<br />\n我就已經向6.12請咗假，作為一個老師，一個香港人，我要為自己同學生負責任，我同學生嘅未來就係掌握係我地所有人嘅手中，6.12罷工，6.11晚立法會見。<br />\n<br />\n你呢？"},{"pid":"5f8b3c2c38023cc88bac273c82e37afcfbbfce44","tid":1198881,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"612考慮中"},{"pid":"13d6fa5c60573c756eeccbd97e843ffa89927ea3","tid":1198881,"uid":199893,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5f8b3c2c38023cc88bac273c82e37afcfbbfce44","tid":1198881,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"612考慮中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗啦，一齊去啦"},{"pid":"3d949322c15fa327e18488dbfc0382367c7be611","tid":1198881,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"小學定中學老師？"},{"pid":"5309de0f7a835f67c1cd3c312b38bb8ed154bb55","tid":1198881,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8b3c2c38023cc88bac273c82e37afcfbbfce44","tid":1198881,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:58:04.000Z","msg":"612考慮中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:06:54.000Z","msg":"考慮得即係心動，心動不如行動，同你嘅老細請個假啦！"},{"pid":"327b313f7dfae4269a2452d9ddbd81198a739bf9","tid":1198881,"uid":26320,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"3d949322c15fa327e18488dbfc0382367c7be611","tid":1198881,"uid":130140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"小學定中學老師？"},"citedBy":0,"repl